    "However, in a multi-class context with an unbalanced dataset, accuracy can be misleading.",
    "To address this, additional metrics were considered.",
    "The F1-score, used in binary classification, balances recall and precision.",
    "It is the harmonic mean of these two measures, providing a comprehensive assessment of the model's ability to identify each class.",
    "The Receiver Operating Characteristic (ROC) curve, crucial for binary classifiers, depicts performance across different discrimination thresholds."
  ],
